node.text:
#PGTrailblazer Makiyo Sagami is leading the innovation behind SKII’s sustainable packaging in Singapore. 

After lots of research, Makiyo and her team decided on bamboo technology for SKII. Makiyo describes herself as a natural and authentic person – which is how she also describes SKII’s sustainable packaging. 

Watch her entire interview (#linkinbio). #PGTrailblazers #PGSignal
